03\/IMG_2357-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_2357-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_2357-1536x2048.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/figure><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-images-slider__item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"http:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-scaled.jpeg\" data-id=\"231\" data-link=\"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/img_7469\/\" data-original-link=\"http:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-scaled.jpeg\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-images-slider__image wp-image-231\" srcset=\"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-scaled.jpeg 1920w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-scaled-600x800.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-225x300.jpeg 225w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/IMG_7469-1536x2048.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/figure><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-e0df0c89 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\"><p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Welcome to the cozy corner of the internet where <strong>Onelia the Korat<\/strong> and <strong>Raika the Irish Soft Coated Wheaten Terrier<\/strong> take center stage. This site is dedicated to sharing the daily lives, personalities, and bond of two very different \u2014 but equally lovable \u2014 companions.<\/p>\n\n<p>What began as a simple idea to capture their cutest moments turned into something more: a space to celebrate the beauty of contrast, companionship, and the joy animals bring to our lives. Whether it\u2019s Raika\u2019s exuberant morning greetings or Onelia\u2019s quiet, contemplative gaze, each moment they share is unique, heartwarming, and often a little funny.<\/p>\n\n<p><strong>Onelia<\/strong>, our striking silver-blue Korat, is all elegance and instinct. Known for her intelligence and watchful nature, she\u2019s independent but affectionate when it matters most. She\u2019s selective, proud, and moves through life with quiet confidence \u2014 a true feline presence that brings calm to our home.<\/p>\n\n<p><strong>Raika<\/strong>, with her soft, tousled coat and endless enthusiasm, brings the sunshine. She\u2019s a classic Wheaten Terrier: cheerful, affectionate, and always ready for the next adventure (or snack). With boundless energy and a heart full of love, Raika is everyone\u2019s best friend \u2014 including, in her own way, Onelia\u2019s.<\/p>\n\n<p>Together, they form an unexpected pair. One is calm, the other lively. One loves silence, the other loves squeaky toys. And yet, in their shared space, a quiet understanding exists. They\u2019ve taught us that friendship doesn\u2019t always look perfect \u2014 but it can be perfectly real.<\/p>\n\n<p>We hope this site brings you the same smiles they bring us every day. Whether you\u2019re a cat person, a dog lover, or simply someone who appreciates the small joys of life with animals, we\u2019re happy to have you here.<\/p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">\u2013 <strong>Team Onelia &amp; Raika<\/strong><\/p><\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Welcome to the cozy corner of the internet where Onelia the Korat and Raika the Irish Soft Coated Wheaten Terrier take center stage. This site is dedicated to sharing the daily lives, personalities, and bond of two very different \u2014 but equally lovable \u2014 companions. What began as a simple idea to capture their cutest [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-no-title","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-464","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/464","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=464"}],"version-history":[{"count":48,"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/464\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":667,"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/464\/revisions\/667"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/onelianraika.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=464"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}